- [ ] All extracted numbers are plain numbers (no commas, no spaces).  
- [ ] Units are exactly as they appear next to the number.  
- [ ] Labels contain the scope name and a total keyword; extra description is kept verbatim.  
- [ ] Every year‑scope pair appears only if a **verified total** was found.  
- [ ] The JSON structure matches the schema exactly.

